    <obo:IAO_0000115 xml:lang="en">ARDS patients with BMI ≥40 kg/m². Elevated chest wall elastance and reduced functional residual capacity alter PEEP requirements substantially. Requires individualised PEEP titration. PROBESE trial enrolled BMI ≥35 (PMID 31157366).</obo:IAO_0000115>
